Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before transitioning to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + In Progress and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + In Progress' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in cases where it directly precedes 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Duration variability of 'Accepted + In Progress' across different resources
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:resource

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' before any transition
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + In Progress' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' leading to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for cases that involve 'Accepted + Wait - User' before resolution
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - User occurs

Name: Average delay time before 'Accepted + In Progress' follows 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in the fastest path to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in the slowest path to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The maximum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' with 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor' to identify process bottlenecks
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for cases that eventually require 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation occurs

Name: Total cumulative duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' for all variants leading to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Distribution of 'Accepted + In Progress' duration across different countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Correlation between the duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' and the time to achieve 'Completed + Resolved' status
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Impact of 'Completed + In Call' activity on the subsequent duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' in a case lifecycle
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + In Progress' during peak incident periods as identified in the VINST system
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time reduction in 'Accepted + In Progress' after implementing changes aimed at improving the 'Completed + In Call' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
